    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I am acting very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But sometimes in the dream, I dreaming all times that I am alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And something happening, and something missing, something take from me the best, good things that I have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So every time I, [CRYING] I looking for my children.",
